flow_desc: The flow begins with the user requesting to create a new group. Initially, they tap the edit icon displayed on the app interface. They then select "New Group" from options available. Following this, the user inputs contacts to be added to the group, tapping on the relevant names displayed with their last seen times. After selecting contacts, the user taps the next button to proceed. They input the desired group name and adjust settings, such as the "Auto-Delete Messages" feature. Finally, they confirm the group creation by tapping the checkmark icon, completing the request successfully.
